blockquote>最主要係機身限制</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n即係800D 唔太掂？</blockquote><br />\n即係crop機高iso弱<br />\n你應該用低iso <br />\n光圈相應就要大但應該用f8最好因為你用好大光圈先會夠光但景深就會淺  咁又唔好  用f5-7就不如直接用f8因為一般鏡頭都係大約f8表現最好<br />\n<br />\n快門就自然冇可能手持  上腳架長曝啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n機身限制意思係要你去circumvent呀  唔係部機廢<br />\n你講個D影得sharp既人未必用好過你好多既機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ebcfc0a7f62aed4a14709923687c529c1078faa","tid":442633,"uid":136044,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-21T04:31:43.000Z","msg":"仲有安全快門夠未<br />\n你用咩焦距影呀<br />\n<br />\n假設冇放手震<br />\n快門最少要1/60 或者 1/焦距<br />\n取快D個個 （即係zoom到近過60mm就用後者）"},{"pid":"20aedae07f0ee9f2acec18194fb8b9e87e626b9a","tid":442633,"uid":56240,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-21T04:32:31.000Z","msg":"垃圾濛，一早block左"},{"pid":"5b7189e3425736212d200acb26ffec9028a0880b","tid":442633,"uid":56240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-21T04:32:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>垃圾濛，一早block左</blockquote><br />\n死臭雞"},{"pid":"ebda970a8d13e79d765f51a7cd80d7dc847ca983","tid":442633,"uid":33497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-21T04:33:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>仲有安全快門夠未<br />\n你用咩焦距影呀<br />\n<br />\n假設冇放手震<br />\n快門最少要1/60 或者 1/焦距<br />\n取快D個個 （即係zoom到近過60mm就用後者）</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10deef57a72e0ca77fe1ee927e82c03533e1c5fe","tid":442633,"uid":97727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-21T06:10:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>之前去左灣仔夜晚影相 返到屋企執相果陣 發覺啲相放大左好濛 以前睇過啲外國Photographers 佢地啲建築物相 就算放到最大都可以見到啲Detail位 我想問下係我既問題定係鏡頭唔夠勁？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n第一您放咁大係為咩先，您取既係意境尼方面就無所謂。如果係想放大聞相，買5d4 5dsr canon / Sony a7r2 / Nikon d850"},{"pid":"1b325073c459f6526dea22642bceb4d89e2f3ae8","tid":442633,"uid":389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sco